OOC: look, my new godarmor has retrorockets. I'm on my way.

Ghost hears a faint distress call coming from bonebreaker's onboard radio.
Ghost: look, goth, I gotta roll out. If you need help with those two new 
godarmors, call.
goth: gotcha!
ghost leaps into the air and calls out " BONEBREAKER: COMBINE!" the large 
grey elephant shifts into armor mode and combines with ghost. ghost powers up 
the retros and blasts off towards ss.

--part1_88.137ce08b.299334c7_boundary
